product.title: Cute Micro Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo Building Sets
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Build your Little World in Little Manhattan with your Iconic Japanese Tofu Shokudo

    Japan prides itself on its yummy food and fascinating decoration from its famous street Tofu Shokudo. Small family restaurant specialist food stores are called Shokudo in Japanese. Now you have the opportunity to experience the life of a Japanese Tofu Shokudo manager opening diners in little Manhattan. 

    🌸 Measurements: varies for each set
    🌸 Not compatible with leading blocks of standard size (16mm), is Micro blocks (12mm)
    🌸 Each set has over 800 micro pieces and varies for each set
    📦 Excludes original box to protect the environment. For further details please see below.*

    We have picked 5 Micro Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo for you to build from scratch, role play, and learn how to run a Japanese street food market in your own room. 

     

    The stores are made with vibrant colored bricks to reflect the modern Japanese society, representing a range of strong emotions; energy, vitality, heat, and power. 

    Our first Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo sells Takahachi Pastry shop. Japanese cakes are creamier and less sweet than Western ones. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains attractive 808 pieces. 

    Our second Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo is Shabu Shabu,  you'll be given plates of meat, vegetables and other items eg dumplings and udon to cook in the broth. It is amazingly fun to cook in front of your friends. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains flaming hot 746 pieces. 

    Our third Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo is Nakazawa Sushi selling their popular delicious Sushi and seafood. Sushi comes from a Japanese word meaning "sour rice," and it's the rice that's at the heart of sushi. A must-try food when you are over in Japan. It contains yummy 753 pieces.

     

    Our forth Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo is Yuzu Sweets store selling desserts and softcream made from natural favours. A must dessert to have after your main meal. A must-try food when you are over in Japan. It contains delicious 713 pieces.

     

    Our final Cute Little Manhattan Japanese Tofu Shokudo is Meow Coffee House. Drinking coffee with a meal can cut down iron absorbed by up to 80 per cent while also reducing the uptake of minerals. It contains refreshing 713 pieces.

    Measurements: about 4in/11cm x 2.5in /6cm  (allow up to 5cm variations in different sets)

    Start building your Japanese Market today by following the instruction booklet.

    The perfect gift for those who love their crafts!

    You will love seeing your family and friends in excitement when they receive our micro building blocks, leaving an everlasting smile on your loved ones by surprising them with this super innovative and cool building blocks today.

    Micro Blocks: Smaller than the traditional building block.


    * Our Building Block sets are packaged in safe and secured protective bags. They do NOT come in the original box to reduce the carbon footprint, save the planet and reduce postage cost on your behalf. It will come with all the pieces and a detailed instruction booklet for you to follow along. 

    Features

    🌸 100% premium quality (ABS) plastic
    🌸 Sharp brilliant colors and solid feel
    🌸 Challenging and rewarding to stimulate all brains
    🌸 High-quality durable non-toxic green material

    WARNING: CHOKING HAZARD - Contain small parts; not suitable for children under 6 years old unless there is adult supervision.


  • Do you ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.

    What are the blocks made from?     All our building blocks are manufactured from a High-Quality Premium strong, resilient plastic known as acrylonitrile butadiene styrene (ABS) and will stand the test of time and provide hours of fun building their own creations

    Does this help with stress and development?     Our building blocks is a great way to relieve stress and engage in meaningful and joyful conversations. As children comment on their building creations, they develop important communication skills including the ability to explain ideas, describe their work, talk about the process and verbalize challenges that they had along the way. 

    CHOKING HAZARD: Small parts. Not for children under 6 years old

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: 5-20 Business days
